				<h2 class="h3 icon-carousel__headline">
					Focus on Future Technologies
				</h2>
			

			
				<p>
					It was from Saxony that European hard porcelain, the first web offset printing press, left-hand drive in the automobile and many other clever ideas began their worldwide triumphal march. Today, Saxon researchers and entrepreneurs are still working hand in hand on intelligent solutions for everyday life.
