								<div class="image-text-carousel__details">
									<p class="image-text-carousel__label">Success Stories</p>
									<h2 class="h3 image-text-carousel__header">
										<a href="/en/bmw-plant-leipzig-sustainability-pioneer" title="Learn more">
											BMW Plant Leipzig: Sustainability Pioneer
										</a>
									</h2>
									<p class="image-text-carousel__text">
										The BMW Plant Leipzig, which opened in 2005, is one of the most modern and sustainable car factories in the world. It is also a pioneer when it comes to electromobility: the BMWi3, the world&#039;s first premium vehicle designed from the ground up for electric drive, was launched on the road from here.
									</p>

									
										<a href="/en/bmw-plant-leipzig-sustainability-pioneer" title="Learn more" class="image-text-carousel__link button button--primary">
											
													Learn more
												
										</a>
									
