											10,000 Million Euros: Semiconductor Manufacturer TSMC Invests in Dresden
										</a>
									</h2>
									<p class="image-text-carousel__text">
										August, 2023: The globally active Taiwanese semiconductor manufacturer TSMC has announced its intention to build a wafer factory in Saxony&#039;s state capital Dresden together with Bosch, Infineon and NXP.
									</p>

									
