			<h2 class="teaser-large__headline">More Than 52,500 Potential Business Partners</h2>

			
				<div class="teaser-large__teaser-text">
					<p>Since 2004, the Saxony Trade &amp; Invest Corporation (WFS - Wirtschaftsförderung Sachsen GmbH) has been operating an online company database. This database currently contains more than 52,500 entries which are maintained and updated by the companies. It is possible, for example, to search the data records for regions, branches, or turnovers.</p>

